<br>
Just thought I would let you know that I went to the Tower of Frozen Shadow and got keys that will let me enter the first three levels of the tower.  This means that I can take a group of people into the tower on a raid if you'd like.  If we get some to go, then we can kill the mobs that drop the keys so that other groups can come in as well.  While I was there, we looted some interesting things.  Gnomeskin armor drops on the third floor and most stuff conned blue-to-yellow to me at level 36 on that floor.  On the second floor, we looted &quot;Student's Homework&quot; which is a range slot item that is +3int +10 sv Magic and +15 mana, but I lost the roll to a monk... grumble grumble grumble...  I'd like to go back and get one of those for myself <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Here is a link to Allakhazam's description of the tower.  It's pretty good.  If you're interested, post here so I can get an idea of how many people we can get to go.  I think you should be at least level 30 to participate.<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/zones/Velious/Tower_of_Frozen_Shadow.html">Tower of Frozen Shadow</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
We need to get a lower-level raid planned.  Perhaps to Unrest, Befallen, or even Crushbone.   Ahem!  Khoal, this is your department as raid-master...<br>
<br>
See you in game soon.<br>
<br>
Gira <p><hr>
